Easy Stretch of Fixtures

Its a pain to identify stretches of appealing fixtures. The coloured indicators that FPL tacked on in 2016-17 dont seem to update with performances.

The charts below try to highlight four aspects that one would typically look for when trying to decide transfers.

The thresholds, etc. arent some sort of recommendation. Feel free to change them if some other number makes more sense.

PS1: I might update this every week or not. PS2: I think this code should be okay with double gameweeks. If it isnt, ll try and fix it at the earliest.
